  "Load BUFFER lines into hash-table BUFFER-TABLE with line-numbers as keys.\n
:SEE `mon-help-hash-functions'.\n
:SEE-ALSO `mon-hash<-vector', `mon-hash-make-size', `mon-hash-add-uniquify',
